question: are creatures with good alignment more common than evil?
query: SELECT ?res  WHERE {  {SELECT (COUNT(?good) as ?n_good)  WHERE{  ?creatures <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasAlignment> ?Alignment  BIND(str(?Alignment) as ?good)  FILTER regex(?good, 'good', 'i')} }  {SELECT (COUNT(?evil) as ?n_evil)  WHERE{ ?creatures <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasAlignment> ?Alignment  BIND(str(?Alignment) as ?evil)  FILTER regex(?evil, 'evil', 'i')} }  BIND(if((?n_good>?n_evil), 'True', 'False') as ?res)  }

question: do dragons in average speak more languages than demons?
query: SELECT (if(AVG(?drag_n_lang)>AVG(?dem_n_lang), 'True', 'False') as ?res) WHERE { {SELECT (COUNT(?language_1) as ?drag_n_lang)  WHERE {   ?creatures_1 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Beast>;  <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasLanguages> ?language_1  FILTER regex(str(?creatures_1),'dragon', 'i')} GROUP BY ?creatures_1} {SELECT (COUNT(?language_2) as ?dem_n_lang)  WHERE {   ?creatures_2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Beast>;  <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasLanguages> ?language_2  FILTER regex(str(?creatures_2),'demon', 'i')} GROUP BY ?creatures_2} }
